new.description: WonderCMS 3.5.0 is vulnerable to a Blind Stored Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) in the homepage content editor. An authenticated attacker can inject arbitrary JavaScript payloads into the homepage content, which will be executed in the context of any user who visits the affected page.
